Do not let the constant evolvement of technology limit today’s decision making, rather have a platform that can grow as you grow. With Yealink Meeting, you can host a meeting with up to 300 participants on various devices such as mobile phones, laptops and video conferencing solutions. Whether you are upgrading your boardroom or expanding to more boardrooms, your workflow remains unaffected. It is as simple as upgrading your software or integrating with Microsoft Teams. Yealink Meeting simplifies video conferencing and collaboration from any device and any space. The seamless integration of Yealink Meeting and Yealink VC endpoints offer a comprehensive solution for all scenarios of 4K video conferencing and wireless content sharing in meeting spaces. Below are Yealink’s Black Friday deals. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-377488 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Picture-1-640x430.png" alt="Small Room Bundle" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Picture-1-640x430.png 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Picture-1-595x400.png 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Picture-1-300x202.png 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Picture-1-768x516.png 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Picture-1-1200x807.png 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Picture-1.png 1416w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> This bundle includes an all-in-one video conferencing bar for small (4-6 seater) boardrooms. You will be able to host 10 simultaneous meetings with up to 300 participants or join a Microsoft Teams meeting. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-377490 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Picture-2-640x430.png" alt="Medium Room Bundle" width=